Filtros básicos

http.request → solicitudes HTTP

tls.handshake.type eq 1 → Client Hello TLS (SNI visible)

(http.request or tls.handshake.type eq 1) and !(ssdp) → tráfico web sin SSDP

Botones de filtro (progresivos)

basic → (http.request or tls.handshake.type eq 1) and !(ssdp)

basic+ → (http.request or tls.handshake.type eq 1 or (tcp.flags.syn eq 1 and tcp.flags.ack eq 0)) and !(ssdp)

basic+dns → (http.request or tls.handshake.type eq 1 or (tcp.flags.syn eq 1 and tcp.flags.ack eq 0) or dns) and !(ssdp)

Protocolos / casos

FTP → ftp (control), ftp-data (datos), ftp.request.command or (ftp-data and tcp.seq eq 1)

SMTP/Spambot → smtp or dns · comandos: smtp.req.command · contenido: smtp.data.fragment

RAT/C2 → usar basic+dns, mirar DNS sospechoso + SYN a puertos raros
